<para>Gets name of the node. Interpretation of name depends on type of node. Note that name will not be zero-terminated if rapidxml::parse_no_string_terminators option was selected during parse. <?linebreak?><?linebreak?> Use <link linkend="_classrapidxml_1_1xml__base_1a20c8ffbe0c7a0b4231681ab8b99330a4">name_size()</link> function to determine length of the name. <formalpara><title>Returns</title>

<para>Name of node, or empty string if node has no name. </para>
</formalpara>
</para>
